                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-bell fa-3x mb-2"></i>
                    <h3>Doświadczenie</h3>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus exercitationem suscipit officiis quos, sapiente nostrum cupiditate odit, quis voluptatem sequi quia tempora quo corporis sint voluptatibus ad! Distinctio, placeat repudiandae.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-power-off fa-3x mb-2"></i>
                    <h3>Jakość</h3>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus exercitationem suscipit officiis quos, sapiente nostrum cupiditate odit, quis voluptatem sequi quia tempora quo corporis sint voluptatibus ad! Distinctio, placeat repudiandae.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>


    <!-- Feature section-->

    <section id="features">
        <div class="container">

            <div class="row section-title justify-content-center mb-4">
                <h2 class="section-title-heading">szczegóły</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-block text-center mb-5">
                        <i class="fas fa-laptop fa-2x mb-2"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-center">Design</h3>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus exercitationem. </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-block text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-download fa-2x mb-2"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-center">Bezpieczeństwo</h3>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus exercitationem. </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="~/img/pomiardb-dev2.png" class="img-fluid" alt="">
                </div>


                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-block text-center mb-5">
                        <i class="fas fa-laptop-house fa-2x mb-2"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-center">Szybkość</h3>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus exercitationem. </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="feature-block text-center">
                        <i class="fas fa-download fa-2x mb-2"></i>
                        <h3 class="text-center">Baza Danych</h3>
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Natus exercitationem. </p>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Download section-->


    <section id="download">

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row download-title justify-content-center">
                <h2>Pobierz aplikację</h2>
                <p>Pobierz aplikację PomiarDB na swoje urządzenie mobilne i już dziś w pełni wykorzystaj potencjał PomiarDB. <br>Wysyłaj i odbieraj pomiary gdziekolwiek jesteś.</p>
                <div class="download-btns">
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-apple"></i> App Store</a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-android"></i> Play Store</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </section>



    <!--Pricing section-->

    <section id="pricing">
        <div class="container">

            <div class="row section-title justify-content-center">
                <h2 class="section-title-heading">PAKIETY</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="row justify-content-center">

                <div class="col-md pricing-table">
                    <div class="table-header text-center">
                        <h4>SMART</h4>
                        <p>25ZŁ/msc</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>free support</li>
                            <li>1gb storage</li>
                            <li>1 users</li>
                            <li>1 email account</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table-footer text-center">
                       
                        @Html.ActionLink("Wybierz", "NewOrder", new { package = 1 },  new {@class = "btn-order"})
                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="col-md pricing-table">

                    <div class="table-header text-center">
                        <h4>PRO</h4>
                        <p>45ZŁ/msc</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>free support</li>
                            <li>20gb storage</li>
                            <li>5 users</li>
                            <li>5 email account</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table-footer text-center">
                        @Html.ActionLink("Wybierz", "NewOrder", new { package = 2 }, new {@class = "btn-order"})
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="col-md pricing-table">

                    <div class="table-header text-center">
                        <h4>GOLD</h4>
                        <p>65ZŁ/msc</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>free support</li>
                            <li>no limit</li>
                            <li>no limit users</li>
                            <li>no limit email account</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="table-footer text-center">
                        @Html.ActionLink("Wybierz", "NewOrder", new { package = 3 }, new {@class="btn-order"})
                    </div>

                </div>


            </div>

        </div>
    </section>



    <!--Contact section-->

    <section id="contact">
        <div class="container">

            <div class="row section-title justify-content-center">
                <h2 class="section-title-heading">Napisz do nas</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="row mt-5">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="contact-form">


                        @using (Html.BeginForm("Send", "Home", FormMethod.Post))
                        {
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col">
                                    @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.FirstName, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Imię" })
                                    @Html.ValidationMessageFor(m => m.FirstName, "", new { @style = "color:red" })
                                </div>
                                <div class="col">
                                    @Html.TextBoxFor(m => m.Email, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Email" })
                                    @Html.ValidationMessageFor(m => m.Email, "", new { @style = "color:red" })
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group mt-4">
                                @Html.TextAreaFor(m => m.Text, new { @class = "form-control", @placeholder = "Wpisz treść wiadomości", @rows = 10 })
                                @Html.ValidationMessageFor(m => m.Text, "", new { @style = "color:red" })
                            </div>

                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-contact mt-4">Wyślij</button>

                        }

                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">

                    <div class="address">
                        <h3>Dane kontaktowe:</h3>
                        <p>Masz pytania ? Skontaktuj się z Nami za pomocą formularza lub telefonicznie. Serdecznie zapraszamy.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-details">
                        <ul class="fa-ul">
                            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i></span>+48 516 302 300</li>
                            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i></span>Katowice</li>
                            <li><span class="fa-li"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i></span>pomiardb@outlook.com</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>




            </div>

        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Footer section -->
    <footer id="footer">

        <div class="container">

            <div class="row d-flex flex-column align-items-center">

                <div class="footer-logo">
                    <img src="~/img/logo.png" alt="obrazek">
                </div>
                <div class="social-icons">
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
                </div>
                <div class="copyright text-center">
                    <p>Copyright 2020</p>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </footer>

    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery.validate.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery.validate.unobtrusive.min.js"></script>

    <script src="~/img/jquery.scrollTo.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/custom.js"></script>


</body>
</html>
